Velmeshev et al. DEGs

velmeshev_gene_df.Rd

From https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.aav8130, data supplement S4 (i.e., aav8130_data-s4.xls)

Usage

velmeshev_gene_df

Format

## `velmeshev_gene_df` A data frame with 692 rows (genes) and 14 columns:

Cell type

gene ID

Gene name

Gene name

Biotype

boolean

boolean
